Mechel Sets $300-a-Ton Coal Price for Posco, IFX Says

-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 
2011-06-15T15:27:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-15/mechel-sets-300-a-ton-coking-coal-price-for-posco-ifx-reports.html
(Corrects price range in second paragraph.)  OAO  Mechel (MTLR)  set a price for supplying
coking coal concentrate to South Korean steel-producer  Posco (005490)  of
$300 a metric ton in the third-quarter, Interfax said, citing an
unidentified person familiar with the deal.  Mechel delivered the fuel at $310 to $325 a ton for spot-
price exports on a free-on-board basis in the second quarter,
Interfax said. Company spokeswoman Ekaterina Videman confirmed
the third-quarter price.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow 
 msysoyeva@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net . 